  <text>
      <body>
         <div type="entry">
            <pb facs="https://leaf.bucknell.edu/sites/default/files/2026-01/diary12.jpg"/>
            <dateline><date><date><date when="1861-12-29">Sunday 29.</date></date></date></dateline>
            <p>We had a <orgName type="company">company</orgName> inspection- then <persName key="Gen Reno" ref="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/BucknellDSC/jmlinn/refs/heads/main/jmlinn_personography.xml">Gen Reno </persName>came &amp; <persName>the Col</persName> understood from him
               that we were to embark tomorrow at twelve o'clock. We were busy this afternoon razeeing down our<objectName type="baggage"> baggage</objectName>. <persName key="George" ref="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/BucknellDSC/jmlinn/refs/heads/main/jmlinn_personography.xml">George</persName> &amp; <persName key="Gib" ref="https://raw.githubusercontent.com/BucknellDSC/jmlinn/refs/heads/main/jmlinn_personography.xml">Gib</persName> went <orgName key="Episcopal Church">to church</orgName> this evening. I stayed at <placeName>home</placeName>
               and wrote some <objectName type="readable">letters</objectName>. We feel quite good in the prospect of marching, if only we
               were a little better drilled.</p>
         </div>
      </body>
  </text>
</TEI>